---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---
<Layout title="Consumer Unit Upgrades | Fuse Box Replacement | MET Electrical" description="Professional consumer unit upgrades in Somerset. Modern RCBOs, surge protection, and enhanced electrical safety. Qualified electrician installations.">
  <main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-brand-yellow text-sm font-medium mb-4">
        <Icon name="tabler:device-tv" class="w-5 h-5" />
        ELECTRICAL SAFETY UPGRADES
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Consumer Unit Upgrades</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/70 max-w-3xl mx-auto">Modern, safer electrical protection with RCBOs, surge protection devices, and enhanced safety features. Professional fuse box replacements across Somerset.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Benefits -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
      <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white/5 rounded-lg border border-white/10">
        <Icon name="tabler:shield-check" class="w-12 h-12 text-brand-yellow mx-auto mb-3" />
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Enhanced Safety</h3>
        <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">RCBOs provide better protection than traditional MCBs</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white/5 rounded-lg border border-white/10">
        <Icon name="tabler:bolt" class="w-12 h-12 text-brand-yellow mx-auto mb-3" />
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Surge Protection</h3>
        <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">SPDs protect your appliances from power surges</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white/5 rounded-lg border border-white/10">
        <Icon name="tabler:tools" class="w-12 h-12 text-brand-yellow mx-auto mb-3" />
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Professional Install</h3>
        <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Tidy, certified installation by qualified electrician</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
      <!-- Main Content -->
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Why Upgrade Your Consumer Unit?</h2>
          <p class="text-white/80 mb-4">An old fuse box or outdated consumer unit may not provide adequate protection for modern electrical demands. Upgrading to a modern consumer unit with RCBOs (Residual Current Breaker with Overcurrent protection) significantly improves electrical safety.</p>
          
          <div class="bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/20 rounded-lg p-4 mb-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <Icon name="tabler:alert-triangle" class="w-6 h-6 text-red-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-red-300 mb-1">Signs You Need an Upgrade</h4>
                <ul class="text-sm text-red-200/80 space-y-1">
                  <li>• Old-style fuse box with wire fuses</li>
                  <li>• No RCD protection</li>
                  <li>• Frequent tripping or electrical faults</li>
                  <li>• Consumer unit over 15+ years old</li>
                  <li>• Insurance requirements</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Modern Consumer Unit Features</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <Icon name="tabler:settings" class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-yellow mt-1 flex-shrink-0" />
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">RCBOs (Recommended)</h3>
                <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Individual circuit protection combining MCB and RCD functionality. If one circuit develops a fault, only that circuit trips - not the whole house.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <Icon name="tabler:bolt" class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-yellow mt-1 flex-shrink-0" />
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Surge Protection Device (SPD)</h3>
                <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Protects your expensive appliances and electronics from power surges caused by lightning or grid switching.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <Icon name="tabler:eye" class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-yellow mt-1 flex-shrink-0" />
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Clear Circuit Labeling</h3>
                <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Professional labeling so you know exactly which circuit controls what in your home.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <Icon name="tabler:certificate" class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-yellow mt-1 flex-shrink-0" />
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Full Certification</h3>
                <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Installation certificate and Building Control notification included.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Our Installation Process</h2>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="bg-brand-blue text-white rounded-full w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-semibold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">1</span>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-medium">Initial Assessment</h4>
                <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Survey your existing installation and electrical requirements</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="bg-brand-blue text-white rounded-full w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-semibold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">2</span>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-medium">Safe Isolation</h4>
                <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Power supply safely isolated and existing unit carefully removed</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="bg-brand-blue text-white rounded-full w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-semibold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">3</span>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-medium">Professional Installation</h4>
                <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">New consumer unit fitted with RCBOs, SPD, and proper labeling</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="bg-brand-blue text-white rounded-full w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-semibold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">4</span>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-medium">Testing & Certification</h4>
                <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Full testing and official certification provided</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>

      <!-- Sidebar -->
      <div class="lg:sticky lg:top-8 space-y-6">
        <!-- Quick Quote -->
        <div class="bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-lg p-6 border border-brand-blue/20">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Get Your Quote</h3>
          <p class="text-white/70 mb-4 text-sm">Professional consumer unit upgrades across Somerset.</p>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <a href="tel:07464336661" class="block w-full btn-primary text-center">Call 07464 336661</a>
            <a href="/contact" class="block w-full btn-secondary text-center">Request Quote</a>
            <a href="https://wa.me/447464336661?text=Hi%2C%20I%20need%20a%20consumer%20unit%20upgrade" class="block w-full btn bg-green-600 text-white hover:bg-green-500 text-center">
              <Icon name="tabler:brand-whatsapp" class="w-4 h-4 mr-1" /> WhatsApp
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Typical Costs -->
        <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-lg p-6 border border-white/10">
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
            <Icon name="tabler:calculator" class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-yellow" />
            Typical Upgrade Options
          </h4>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
              <div>
                <div class="font-medium">Basic MCB + RCD</div>
                <div class="text-white/60 text-xs">Traditional split-load design</div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-brand-yellow font-medium">From £400</div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
              <div>
                <div class="font-medium">RCBO + SPD</div>
                <div class="text-white/60 text-xs">Individual circuit protection</div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-brand-yellow font-medium">From £650</div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
              <div>
                <div class="font-medium">High-spec RCBO</div>
                <div class="text-white/60 text-xs">Premium components & SPD</div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-brand-yellow font-medium">From £850</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-white/50 mt-3">*Prices exclude VAT and depend on specific requirements</p>
        </div>

        <!-- What's Included -->
        <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-lg p-6 border border-white/10">
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
            <Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-yellow" />
            What's Included
          </h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-white/80">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-yellow flex-shrink-0"></span>
              New consumer unit with RCBOs
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-yellow flex-shrink-0"></span>
              Surge protection device (SPD)
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-yellow flex-shrink-0"></span>
              Professional circuit labeling
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-yellow flex-shrink-0"></span>
              Full testing & certification
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-yellow flex-shrink-0"></span>
              Building Control notification
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-yellow flex-shrink-0"></span>
              Tidy installation & cleanup
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section class="mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">How long does an upgrade take?</h4>
            <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Most consumer unit upgrades are completed in 4-6 hours, often done in a single day with power restored the same day.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Will I be without power?</h4>
            <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Yes, power will be off during installation. We work efficiently to minimize disruption, typically 4-6 hours total.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Do I need Building Control approval?</h4>
            <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">We handle all Building Control notifications as part of our service - no extra paperwork for you.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">What's the difference between MCBs and RCBOs?</h4>
            <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">RCBOs provide individual earth leakage protection per circuit, whereas MCBs rely on a shared RCD. RCBOs offer better fault isolation.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Is surge protection necessary?</h4>
            <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">While not legally required, SPDs protect expensive appliances and electronics from power surges. Increasingly recommended by electricians.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">How often should consumer units be replaced?</h4>
            <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Modern consumer units typically last 20+ years, but units over 15 years old may benefit from upgrading to current safety standards.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Back to Services -->
    <div class="mt-12 text-center">
      <a href="/services" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-brand-yellow hover:text-white transition">
        <Icon name="tabler:arrow-left" class="w-4 h-4" />
        Back to All Services
      </a>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>